<li><a href="/wiki/Sharon_White" title="Sharon White" class="mw-redirect">Sharon White</a> - backing vocals</li>
</ul>
<p>Support act for European and US / Canada&#160;: The <a href="/wiki/Robert_Cray" title="Robert Cray">Robert Cray</a> Band</p>
<p><a name="2008_Summer_Tour_Band" id="2008_Summer_Tour_Band"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Eric_Clapton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=22" title="Edit section: 2008 Summer Tour Band">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">2008 Summer Tour Band</span></h3>
<p>Eastern U.S. / Canada Tour</p>
<ul>
<li><strong class="selflink">Eric Clapton</strong> (guitar / vocals)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Doyle_Bramhall_II" title="Doyle Bramhall II">Doyle Bramhall II</a> (guitar / backing vocals)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Chris_Stainton" title="Chris Stainton">Chris Stainton</a> (keyboards)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Pino_Palladino" title="Pino Palladino">Pino Palladino</a> (bass)</li>
